def insert_after_index(lst):
    index = lst.index(44)
    lst.insert(index+1, [40, 27])
    return lst

# Example usage
given_list = [1, 2, 3, 4, 44, 5, 6, 7]
result_list = insert_after_index(given_list)
print(result_list)
